    </div>
    <div type="creationmaintenance">
        <!-- PREMIS Creation / Maintenance -->
        <p>This value could be supplied by the submitter or by the repository. If
            environment software and hardware information is obtained from an
            environment registry, <boldi>relatedEnvironmentCharacteristic</boldi> might
            also be obtained from the registry. Note however that the criteria for
            “recommended” may be different for different repositories.</p>
    </div>
